{
  "stem": "24171.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he brought us a few words-- not to worry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We are by-- I don't remember who-- what, he didn't said Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But so we knew that-- no, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- now I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had, in-- in Munkacs, we knew a guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was a-- a communist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he went-- you know, some of the communists went to Russia when it just started, kinda-- the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he wrote, he is not where [NON-ENGLISH] is, from Munkacs, you know, from Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew that he is in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we are in-- we were in seventh heaven that they are in Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are not already under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we thought that they gonna come home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what do the Russians do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't believe for nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They kept all those-- which, running away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So which they catched from whoever, you know-- thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They went Siberia-- they put them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I don't know how long they were there in Siberia, or what it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was wanting-- no, wanting that, you know, that there was a Czech legion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When-- when the Russians start going against Hitler, you know, when they were not anymore friends with them, there was a lot of Jewish boys-- even not Jewish-- you know, which formed a Czech legion in Russia.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went to help for the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had their own whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I don't know who was in command.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians were in command.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my two brothers were in that legion too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the one, [NON-ENGLISH] you know, from Prague, he was a very kind of delicate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was kind of like a city boy, because he went away from home by 18.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He went to school, to Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
